ng\" style=\"width: 270px; height: 152px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Đào tạo tâm thế, chuyên môn</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload_images/images/2020/03/11/nang-luc8.png\" style=\"width: 270px; height: 152px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Xây dựng môi trường làm việc an toàn, hiệu quả</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload_images/images/2020/03/11/nang-luc9.png\" style=\"width: 270px; height: 152px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Cung cấp sản phẩm hoàn chỉnh đáp ứng nhu cầu khắt khe của khách hàng</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col col-md-3\">\r\n<div class=\"content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/upload_images/images/2020/03/11/nang-luc10.png\" style=\"width: 270px; height: 152px;\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Giá trị khác</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style type=\"text/css\">.mo-hinh-item{ \r\n	background-color:#fff;\r\n	border:1px solid #76c3ec;\r\n	border-radius:10px;\r\n	float:left; \r\n	width:20%;\r\n	height:130px;}\r\n.mo-hinh-content{\r\n	padding:20px 20px;\r\n	text-align:center;\r\n}\r\n.mo-hinh-item-hidden{\r\n	float:left; \r\n	width:20%;\r\n	height:130px;}\r\n.mo-hinh-muiten{\r\n	margin-top:50px;\r\n	float:left; \r\n	width:6%;}\r\n.mo-hinh-muiten p{ text-align:center;}\r\n.row-2{ margin-top:20px;}\r\n.pc-hidden{display:none;}\r\n@media (max-width:768px){\r\n.mo-hinh{ margin-left:20px;}\r\n.mo-hinh-item{ \r\n	width:40%;\r\n	height:170px;\r\n	}\r\n.mo-hinh-muiten{\r\n	margin-top:50px;\r\n	float:left; \r\n	width:10%;}\r\n.mobile-hidden { display:none;}\r\n.pc-hidden{     display: block;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    height: 20px;\r\n    clear: both;}\r\n.col-md-3 .content p{ text-align:center;}\r\n.mo