der-box\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial !important\"><span style=\"color:#333333 !important\"><span style=\"line-height:2 !important\"><span style=\"background-color:initial\">- Môi trường làm việc tốt, công việc đảm bảo ổn định, lâu dài.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin:0px !important; padding:0px !important; text-align:left; -webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px !important\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"color:#333333 !important\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial !important\"><span style=\"line-height:2 !important\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-line\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"position:relative\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><span style=\"line-height:2 !important\"><span style=\"transition:all 0.2s ease-in 0s\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial\"><span style=\"font-style:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures:normal\"><span style=\"font-variant-caps:normal\"><span style=\"font-weight:400\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:normal\"><span style=\"orphans:2\"><span style=\"text-transform:none\"><span style=\"white-space:pre-line\"><span style=\"widows:2\"><span style=\"word-spacing:0px\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\"><span style=\"text-decoration-style:initial\"><span style=\"text-decoration-color:initial\"><span style=\"font-size:14px !important; margin:0px !important; padding:0px !important\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial !important\"><span style=\"color:#333333 !important\"><span style=\"line-height:2 !important\"><span style=\"background-color:initial\">- Được ghi nhận thành tích, được khen thưởng, có cơ hội thăng tiến, phát triển nghề nghiệp.&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></sp